                'content' => '<ul><li><strong>Reduced Stress</strong> - Staff transition from tedious data entry to meaningful work</li><li><strong>Scalability</strong> - Accommodate growth without workflow reinvention</li><li><strong>Better Vendor Relationships</strong> - Timely, accurate accounts payable and early payment discounts</li><li><strong>Improved Audit Readiness</strong> - Clean records with clear transaction trails</li><li><strong>Increased Credibility</strong> - Professional accounting practices impress lenders and investors</li></ul>'
