                'content' => '<p><strong>Initial Consultation</strong> - The bookkeeping firm learns your business structure, services, staffing, systems, and pain points.</p><p><strong>Data Import</strong> - Access to bank accounts, statements, payroll records, inventory lists, and historical invoices.</p><p><strong>Software Setup</strong> - Connect shop management to accounting software with proper field mapping.</p><p><strong>Process Definition</strong> - Establish invoice submission protocols, payment approval workflows, and reporting frequency.</p><p><strong>Training</strong> - Owners, managers, and service writers learn submission procedures and report interpretation.</p><p><strong>Monthly Workflow</strong> - Account reconciliation, deposit matching, payroll processing, vendor payments, and statement preparation.</p>'
