                'id' => 'digital-features',
                'title' => 'Features of Digital Labor Guides',
                'content' => '<ul><li><strong>VIN-Specific Labor Times</strong> - Tailored to exact vehicle configuration and engine architecture</li><li><strong>Parts Integration</strong> - Suggestions and pricing based on vendor catalogs with core charges</li><li><strong>Pre-Written Repair Stories</strong> - Step-by-step instructions, tools, torque specs, diagrams</li><li><strong>Continuous Updates</strong> - Cloud-based updates with access from any device</li><li><strong>Work Order Integration</strong> - Labor hours flow directly into estimates and invoices</li><li><strong>AI Enhancements</strong> - Learn from your shop\'s actual labor times</li></ul>'
