                'content' => '<p><strong>Shop A - 10-Bay Diesel Repair:</strong> Increased labor revenue by 12% on complex jobs, reduced estimate time by 60%, fewer customer disputes.</p><p><strong>Shop B - Medium-Duty Service Center:</strong> Added $9,000 per month in recovered labor, reduced turnaround time, trained new service writers in half the time.</p><p><strong>Shop C - Trailer Repair Facility:</strong> Customer complaints about surprise hours dropped 70%, better scheduling reduced overtime, improved customer satisfaction and repeat business.</p>'
